{"tid":2139098,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"處理625萬樣本 毋須專業醫護完成  英快速武肺測試 90分鐘有結果","createTime":"2020-08-04T05:18:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T06:08:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2f4854d3a089bfa5d52f00cf056d28d811adb234","tid":2139098,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T05:18:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200804/SITYUYC25KSCOS4LEIT6IJGNBE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200804%2FSITYUYC25KSCOS4LEIT6IJGNBE%2F&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4Yd4vgSq%2BgcR%2FX%2FBaLnjou7zI%3D&h=b20b7233\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200804%2FSITYUYC25KSCOS4LEIT6IJGNBE%2F&h=8464e728\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200804/SITYUYC25KSCOS4LEIT6IJGNBE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n處理625萬樣本 毋須專業醫護完成 <br />\n英快速武肺測試 90分鐘有結果<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/QH7VABSx02L_CAuGryALtQ_P46g=/988x650/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FXLFH6EBHMAO54A5U5PQEB4BQU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQH7VABSx02L_CAuGryALtQ_P46g%3D%2F988x650%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFXLFH6EBHMAO54A5U5PQEB4BQU.jpg&h=d5cd6994&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nNudgeBox分析儀只有鞋盒般大小，收集樣本的匣子亦只有碳粉匣那麼大。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。，可望到10月尾達每日50萬次檢測目標。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：伊朗隱瞞疫情4.2萬人病歿<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。；只需於鼻孔輕輕抹片，一小時內儀器便可分析病人的DNA是否有武肺病毒，找尋當中是否含有武漢肺炎病毒的核糖核酸（RNA）基因物料，也可測出流感等其他呼吸系統疾病。毋須送交化驗室便有結果，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/T7IM8lu1ZXF7lQbH3z2ZOPbeySM=/660x407/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XWOXJAGW3YD2P32ICNV7IPTIQI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FT7IM8lu1ZXF7lQbH3z2ZOPbeySM%3D%2F660x407%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXWOXJAGW3YD2P32ICNV7IPTIQI.jpg&h=620ae508&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n倫敦大學帝國學院白城分校是DNA Nudge總部所在地。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/BaGh679H4dEHF9ilFzzWIl-vKlQ=/672x465/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CVNNI3EMTBWGVS5WA2543KGZDI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBaGh679H4dEHF9ilFzzWIl-vKlQ%3D%2F672x465%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCVNNI3EMTBWGVS5WA2543KGZDI.jpg&h=6d3ab0dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖瑪佐教授領導DNA Nudge研發團隊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不用深喉測試減難度<br />\n<br />\nNudgeBox另一好處是操作簡易，普通人都可以應付；毋須抽取鼻液或深喉測試，減低難度，不會因為測試程序出錯影響準確度。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另外，政府會在實驗室和臨時中心提供另一款由牛津大學旗下公司研發的LamPORE測試，該測試可辨認未出現徵狀或無病徵個案，亦可判斷樣本蒐集時是否足夠，減少「假陰性」結果。測試可用兩種尺寸機器分析，60至90分鐘有結果，大機約打印機大小，一天可分析15,000份樣本，稍後計劃推廣到機場，為入境旅客作測試；細機只有釘書機大小，一天處理2,000樣本，擬用於學校和護養院。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n盼入秋日檢測50萬人<br />\n<br />\n衞生大臣夏國賢昨日公佈詳情時，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n目前英國當局一天可處理22萬人次的測試，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n英國爆疫至今，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n路透社／英國《泰晤士報》"},{"pid":"704d7f22e08d60088b0ecfcf65fe788694f12218","tid":2139098,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T06:08:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/awmjKcQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FawmjKcQ.gif&h=74873027&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}